[color=blue] [What does it do?][/color]

It changes Silda The Unseen's clothes to fine clothes, and she is no longer a beggar.


[color=red] [Where can I find her?][/color]

CandleHearth Hall, In Windhelm.


[GOALS FOR ALL MY MODS]

To have any of my mods reviewed by youtubers such as Brodual, and MMOxReview.


[color=yellow] [MANUALLY INSTALLING][/color]

Go to you're steam file steam/steamapps/commen/skyrim/data and drop my file in ur skyrim data.




Enjoy
